#1. Create a greeting for your program.
print("Hello! Welcome to the Band Name Generator!")
#2. Ask the user for the city that they grew up in, input cursor should be on a new line.
city_name = input("What city did you grow up in?\n")
#3. Ask the user for the name of a pet, input cursor should be on a new line.
pet_name = input("What is/was the name of your pet?\n")
#4. Combine the name of their city and pet and show them their band name.
print("You could call your band " + city_name + " " + pet_name + "!\n")


